{"srs_requirement_key": "WEBOSKSRS-1085", "title": "languageStyle", "srs_key": "WEBOSKSRS-1083", "feature": "Basic.Internationalization.Language", "category": null, "input_output_relationship": "<p>입력 : 현재 locale 명</p>\r\n\r\n<p>출력 : font 정보</p>\r\n", "normal_operation": "<div class=\"content-wrapper\">\r\n<p><span class=\"conf-macro output-inline\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-name=\"text-data\">font family, weight, size 사용 시의 규칙을 UI control 별로, 로케일 별로, 제공할 수 있는 인터페이스 제공. 관련 epic/story/test case는 아래 참고</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://jira2.lgsvl.com/browse/DRD4TV-657\">https://jira2.lgsvl.com/browse/DRD4TV-657</a>&nbsp;<span class=\"conf-macro output-inline\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-name=\"text-data\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>아래 정보를 따라 font정보를 리턴함.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://wiki.lgsvl.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=146029254\">https://wiki.lgsvl.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=146029254</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n", "alternative_motion": "<p>없음</p>\r\n", "exception_handling": "<p>없음.</p>\r\n", "soc": "[\"SoC 공통\"]", "region": "[\"Global 공통\", \"TBD\"]", "tc_id_list": "[\"NA\"]", "change_type": "기존"}
{"srs_requirement_key": "WEBOSKSRS-2830", "title": "CP로그인 Relay Server 구축", "srs_key": "WEBOSKSRS-2811", "feature": "Basic.Settings.WizardSetting-FirstUse", "category": null, "input_output_relationship": "<p><b>Pre-condition</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Network 연결, 기본 약관 동의</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.입력: Device Rest Call Parameter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. 출력: Server Rest Response</p>\r\n", "normal_operation": "<p>연동규격에 따른 요청/응답</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lt;Pre-condition&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>URL:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 102); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\">https://</span><em style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 102); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\">{phase:qt2-kic}</em><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 102); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\">.cpauth.lgtvcommon.com/auth/</span><em style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 102); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;\">{version:v1.0}</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><b>1.&nbsp;{URL}<font color=\"#003366\" face=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif\">/initiation</font></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; 1-1. {URL}<font color=\"#003366\" face=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif\">/initiation 형태로 아래의 Parameter로 REST Call을 받는다.&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"brush: java;\" contenteditable=\"false\" name=\"code\" style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7;border:1px solid #d7d7d7;padding:.5em 1em .5em 1em;\">{\r\n    \"appId\":\"amazon\",\r\n    \"deviceId\":\"deviceId\",\r\n    \"deviceType\":\"deviceType\"\r\n}</pre>\r\n\r\n<p><font color=\"#003366\" face=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif\">&nbsp; 1-2. Response Code 200과 함께 아래의 Response Body를 전달받는다.&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"brush: java;\" contenteditable=\"false\" name=\"code\" style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7;border:1px solid #d7d7d7;padding:.5em 1em .5em 1em;\">{\r\n    \"appId\":\"amazon\",\r\n    \"verificationUrl\":\"https://host/sample\",\r\n    \"userCode\":\"ABC123\",\r\n    \"deviceCode\":\"911b9c44-a3e9-46f3-ab55-0adbe782a83e\",\r\n    \"expiresIn\":600,\r\n    \"payload\":{...}\r\n}</pre>\r\n\r\n<p><b><font color=\"#003366\" face=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif\">2. </font>{URL}<font color=\"#003366\" face=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif\">/completion</font></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2-1. {URL}<font color=\"#003366\" face=\"-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif\">/completion 형태로 아래의 Parameter로 REST Call을 받는다.&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n\r\n<pre class=\"brush: java;\" contenteditable=\"false\" name=\"code\" style=\"background-color:#f7f7f7;border:1px solid #d7d7d7;padding:.5em 1em .5em 1em;\">{\r\n    \"appId\":\"amazon\",\r\n    \"deviceType\":\"deviceType\",\r\n    \"deviceId\":\"deviceid\",\r\n    \"userCode\":\"ABC123\",\r\n    \"privateCode\":\"911b9c44-a3e9-46f3-ab55-0adbe782a83e\"\r\n    \"payload\":{...}\r\n}</pre>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 102); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica 